{"title":"敲石者","authors":["袁冬青"],"dates":[{"year":1988,"month":1,"day":5}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"敲石者"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"袁冬青"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敲出火星"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敲出叮当的诱惑声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敲出硬邦邦的筋骨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敲出汗淋淋的故事"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生活就是他们敲出的带彩石块"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"石块是他们发咸汗水的结晶体"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敲石敲开铜雕的银行大门"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"保险库储存起他们的希望"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们的希望是用汗水积赚的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"虚幻的梦终于不再是梦幻"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敲石敲出农村"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敲出城市"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"现代化的立体建筑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敲醒每一块沉睡的石头"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中华民族的脊梁——长城"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在叮叮当当的诱惑声中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"醒来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它展示着一个真理"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"世界是民众敲出来的呀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敲石者绷紧的神经里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"隐藏着丰厚的敲不完的财富"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}